// through the new StreamCorec recognizer + lowering. The Cryptol
// `xs = [True] # xs` lowers to `fix (Stream Bool) (\rec -> MkStream
// Bool (\i -> ...))` after scNormalize, the recognizer matches it,
// and the lowering emits `mkStreamFix Bool (error _) ...` instead of
// rejecting via L-5.
//
